show.title: Echoes Of Vengeance
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/dVZ2PG
show.description: When ambitious Elara crosses paths with the enigmatic Damon at a high-profile fashion show, she sees more than just another industry power player—she sees her chance for revenge. Armed with an old grudge and cold determination, she infiltrates his glamorous world, intent on making him pay for past wrongs. But as the lines between vengeance and attraction blur, Elara discovers layers to Damon she never expected. Amid the glittering backdrop of runways and galas, she's forced to confront an unsettling question: is her thirst for retribution justified, or is she destroying something that could heal them both? In this stylish tale of revenge and redemption, the price of settling old scores might be higher than either can afford.
